Name: Child of Aquarius
Description:
An impossibly delicate jellyfish. Its tentacles are as fine as strands of hair, its entire being glassy, dancing on the edge of what is possible.

A gift from the sea, almost too precious to keep...

Name: Spawn of Arcadia
Description:
A glassy jellyfish, lights pulsing beneath its skin. Its thin tentacles pluck at the air, their vibrations manipulating the space around its body.

As it writhes, a faint music drifts from its tendrils, worming its way into your ears. The melody seems to never end, worming its way into your ears, never ending, worming its way into your ears, never ending, never...

Name: The Angler
Description:
Fire dances across the scales of this impossible marine being. Its starlit eyes stare back at you with a meaning far deeper than any fish should know. As they stare, the world around you fades away.

The sound of water fills your ears. It wants to be free. You want to be free...

Use [E] to unseal the bottle and read the message within.
